The Premier League has expanded its international presence with the launch of an office in Beijing, adding to its existing offices in London and Mumbai. summary: Real Madrid had a successful week, claiming victory in the Women's Champions League with a 4-0 win over Celtic. However, there are reports of regret over the signing of Kylian Mbappe, with claims that only one key figure within the club supported the move. Real Madrid also celebrated another 4-0 victory against Celtic Women, while Celtic Women's team suffered a loss against Real Madrid Femenino. An injury update ahead of the Celta Vigo match reveals the status of Vinicius Junior and Eder Militao. Finally, Real Madrid and adidas have collaborated on an "Artist Pack" collection.
